 Proposal

## What will (likely) be the title of your project?

Quarentine Cards!

## In just a sentence or two, summarize your project. (E.g., "A website that lets you buy and sell stocks.")

For the project, I would really like to code a website. The website will pretty much be an E-card generator. It will be themed, becuase we are in quarentine. So it'll be updates to send to friends and loved ones.

## In a paragraph or more, detail your project. What will your software do? What features will it have? How will it be executed?

The purpose of the project is to build a generator that will allow for the user to customize thier own E-card. With us being in quarentine, the E-cards could be updates on what you're doing inside in quarentine, because social settings have been limited.
It will be written in python, I also plan on trying to incorporate some CSS or HTML to make the website more pleasing to look at and use. The user will be able to pick the color of the card, add photos, or use stickers/photos from the gallery I will provide.
A text box to write a note, and lastly they will be able to  send it to people. If I can I would like to include a search bar that will find a song that you would like to include. And it will include a little barcode on the bottom of the card. So when the recipient gets the card, 
they can scan it and it will bring up the song the user wanted. 

