## In the world of software, most everything takes longer to implement than you expect. And so it's not uncommon to accomplish less in a fixed amount of time than you hope.

### In a sentence (or list of features), define a GOOD outcome for your final project. I.e., what WILL you accomplish no matter what?

I'd really like to be able to make the website, have the user be able to customize a card, and send it to their desired recipient. I might not be able to add the scanning part with the music at the end. 

### In a sentence (or list of features), define a BETTER outcome for your final project. I.e., what do you THINK you can accomplish before the final project's deadline?

Everthing including the scanning part for the song. 

### In a sentence (or list of features), define a BEST outcome for your final project. I.e., what do you HOPE to accomplish before the final project's deadline?

For the absolute best outcome, I would like to have everything that I planned mentioned- including the scanning part, and more. Specifically, I would like for the user to be able to include videos as well as photos. 
I'm not sure if that will allow it, hopefully it will. 

## In a paragraph or more, outline your next steps. What new skills will you need to acquire? What topics will you need to research? If working with one of two classmates, who will do what?
Besides coding the website, I need to become very good at CSS and HTML because those are necessary for the user experience to be enjoyable. I need to somehow learn how to connect with API's that 
will allow for me to have a search bar that can find songs for the scanning/barcode portion of the card. 


